    },
    {
      "id": "6084d68855cbd30000342f20",
      "text": "https://twitter.com/hideman2009/status/1386139935292289024",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1619318409,
      "updated": 1619318409
    },
    {
      "id": "6084d64455cbd30000342f1d",
      "text": ">我々が，「頭でものを考えること」を”内言”と呼びます．一方，この内言は，一人ひとり，全く異なる特性を持っていることが知られています．例えば，「”[声]”で物事を考える人」，「”[映像]”で物事を考える人」，「”[文字]”で物事を考える人」，「前述のものとは全く異なる方法で物事を考える人」など，人によって内言の中身やその方法は，千差万別です",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619318341,
      "updated": 1619354319
    },
    {
      "id": "6084d64455cbd30000342f1e",
      "text": " そうなんだ！[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1619318341,
      "updated": 1619318699
    },
    {
      "id": "6084f28555cbd30000342f34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1619325574,
      "updated": 1619325574
    },
    {
      "id": "6084f28555cbd30000342f35",
      "text": "あなたの内言は",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1619325574,
      "updated": 1619325589
    },
    {
      "id": "6084f28b55cbd30000342f36",
      "text": "　声[mtane0412.icon][yosider.icon][takker.icon][imo.icon][rickshinmi.icon][sta.icon][maichan.icon][mizdra.icon][dai.icon][teyoda7.icon]",
      "userId": "6171231417617a001d7c8c6d",
      "created": 1619325579,
      "updated": 1646540074
    },
    {
      "id": "608562b3e5172d0000fb1838",
      "text": "　　映像も思い浮かぶけどメインは声な気がする[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619354291,
      "updated": 1619354291
    },
    {
      "id": "6084f28c55cbd30000342f37",
      "text": "　映像[mtane0412.icon][yosider.icon][takker.icon][erniogi.icon][U.icon][maichan.icon]",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1619325580,
      "updated": 1633625823
    },
    {
      "id": "6084f28e55cbd30000342f38",
      "text": "　\t出来なくはないが苦手[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1619325583,
      "updated": 1619361987
    },
    {
      "id": "6150f0c379d3a90000dda77f",
      "text": "　\tできてるか自信ない[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1632694468,
      "updated": 1632694479
    },
    {
      "id": "6150f0ce79d3a90000dda780",
      "text": "　\t\t[アファンタジア]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1632694479,
      "updated": 1632694482
    },
    {
      "id": "60857fbe06848400009f1801",
      "text": "　文字",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1619361727,
      "updated": 1632694006
    },
    {
      "id": "6150eef679d3a90000dda77a",
      "text": "　その他",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1632694007,
      "updated": 1632694091
    },
    {
      "id": "6086907ae5172d0000e73d67",
      "text": "　　食べたときの[味覚]の想像もする[yosider.icon][maichan.icon]",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1619431547,
      "updated": 1633625867
    },
    {
      "id": "615076e38ee92a0000f0d342",
      "text": "　　イメージがわかない [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1632663268,
      "updated": 1632663272
    },
    {
      "id": "615077098ee92a0000f0d343",
      "text": "　　 「頭でものを考えること」をしないのだろうか?",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1632663306,
      "updated": 1632663311
    },
    {
      "id": "615077138ee92a0000f0d344",
      "text": "　　 そんなワケはないか",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1632663316,
      "updated": 1632663319
    },
    {
      "id": "615f274dc3f2c700009c93d0",
      "text": "　　匂いや肌触りなども想像します[maichan.icon]",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1633625934,
      "updated": 1633625989
    },
    {
      "id": "6084d64f55cbd30000342f1f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1632694505,
      "updated": 1632694560
    },
    {
      "id": "6160610f385a920000b06695",
      "text": "　考える対象によって違うのでは？[miyamonz.icon]",
      "userId": "5953adab7aa58a0011385a92",
      "created": 1633706256,
      "updated": 1633706263
    },
    {
      "id": "61606117385a920000b06696",
      "text": "　　物事の概念を考えるとき、声でも文字でも無い気がするが、よくわからない[miyamonz.icon]",
      "userId": "5953adab7aa58a0011385a92",
      "created": 1633706263,
      "updated": 1633706290
    },
    {
      "id": "6160610f385a920000b06694",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5953adab7aa58a0011385a92",
      "created": 1633706255,
      "updated": 1633706255
    },
    {
      "id": "6084d68a55cbd30000342f21",
      "text": "[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7EpAc9DeOfY]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1619318411,
      "updated": 1619318428
    },
    {
      "id": "6084d69b55cbd30000342f23",
